{"article_id":"1E6ib7Fsd6GT8ALU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Michael Bloomberg has finally decided to run for president ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after a years-long game of will-he-or-won ' t-he .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"On Sunday , the 77-year-old billionaire philanthropist , media magnate , and former New York City mayor officially announced","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"he will campaign","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to win the White House in the Democratic primary .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Earlier this month , rumblings began","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that Bloomberg would finally pull the trigger","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"after he started to register","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"to get on the ballot in multiple states .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"He further fueled speculation","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"when he apologized on November 17 for his mayoral administration ' s stop-and-frisk policy ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"after declining to do so for years .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"It ' s been a long road to get here .","depth":3},{"id":13,"text":"In March , Bloomberg said","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"he wouldn ' t run for president .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"He also publicly ruled out an independent bid back in 2016 .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"But now , he ' s going to go for it after all .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"\" I ' m running for president","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to defeat Donald Trump","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and rebuild America , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Bloomberg said in a Sunday statement .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" We can not afford four more years of President Trump ' s reckless and unethical actions . ...","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"If he wins another term in office ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"we may never recover from the damage . \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"In the face of the rise of progressive candidates like Sens . Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren and the perceived weakness of former Vice President Joe Biden ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Bloomberg appears to be tossing his hat in the ring as a moderate alternative .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Though he switched his affiliation back to the Democratic Party in 2018 after years as a Republican and independent ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that doesn ' t mean he ' s all-in on the progressive issues","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"other Democrats are embracing ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"as I noted earlier this month :","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"He is a champion of gun control and addressing climate change ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"but he has criticized Medicare-for-all as unaffordable","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Warren ' s proposed wealth tax is likely unconstitutional .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"He has expressed optimism about the Green New Deal","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"all of the concepts in it deserve consideration ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"but warned","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that it should not put forth \" things","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that are pie in the sky. \"","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"He is viewed as a more Wall Street-friendly , centrist candidate .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"Bloomberg ' s run hasn ' t been met with , say , the most open arms among the Democratic base .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"A Morning Consult poll","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"conducted","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"soon after the Bloomberg buzz started earlier this month","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"found that just 4 percent of Democratic primary voters would pick the former mayor as their first choice","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"to be the party ' s nominee ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"behind Biden , Sanders , Warren , Pete Buttigieg , and Kamala Harris .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"In a head-to-head poll with President Donald Trump , Bloomberg did have a lead over the current president ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"as did Warren , Sanders , and Biden .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Other candidates have criticized Bloomberg","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"over weighing entering the race","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"and held him up as another example of a billionaire","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"trying to exert too much influence over politics ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"as Riley Beggin laid out for :","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"who was campaigning with one of his key surrogates","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"- Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez -","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"in Iowa ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"told supporters ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"\" You ' re not going to buy this election","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"by spending hundreds of millions of dollars on media in California. \"","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"Ocasio-Cortez later told reporters ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"\" They ' ve got class solidarity .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"The billionaires are looking out for each other .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"They ' re willing to transcend difference and background and even politics. \"","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"And Sanders echoed that sentiment ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" Jeff Bezos ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"worth $ 150 billion , supporting Mike Bloomberg ,","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"who ' s worth only $ 50 billion ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"that ' s real class solidarity. \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Sen. Elizabeth Warren ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"who has called for taxing assets over $ 1 billion at 6 percent ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"also skewered Bloomberg","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"following reports of the call ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"writing on Twitter ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" One billionaire calls another billionaire","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"and asks him to run for president","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"- I ' m shocked ! \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"She also linked to a wealth calculator","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"showing how much billionaires would pay under her proposed wealth tax","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"( there ' s a button","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"where visitors can choose to be Bloomberg , among others ) .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Biden told reporters prior to Bloomberg ' s announcement","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"that he has \" no problem \" with him getting into the race .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"\" In terms","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"of he ' s running","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"because of me ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"the last polls","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"I looked at ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"I ' m pretty far ahead , \"","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Of course , not everyone was so turned off by the idea of a Bloomberg run","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"- including , and perhaps especially , many of those in the same tax bracket .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Hedge funder Leon Cooperman ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"who has been publicly feuding with Warren ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"told CNBC","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he would back his fellow billionaire .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Recode ' s Jason Del Rey reported","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos had put in a call months earlier","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"to ask Bloomberg","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"if he would make a White House run .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Ben White at Politico reported","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that many on Wall Street have an affinity for Bloomberg","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"but were well aware","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"his candidacy was a long shot , to say the least .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"White quoted one senior Wall Street executive","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"it is \" ridiculous \" for him to think","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"he can win the Democratic nomination .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"he could wish on a star","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"that the process is different , \"","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"the executive said .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"\" But it ' s not . \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Bloomberg ' s presidential bid may have the opposite of the effect","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"he intended","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"- namely , boosting progressive candidates such as Warren and Sanders","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"and eating up support from moderates like Biden and Buttigieg .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"' s Matt Yglesias laid out the issue :","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"The key is that in recent years , moderates","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"who ' ve successfully fended off the left wing of the Democratic Party","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"have done so with the support of black and Latino voters ,","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"who tend to be more moderate on the whole than white Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"But Bloomberg ' s specific political career gives him little access to this constituency and thus little hope","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"of securing the nomination .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"What he can do is compete with Biden","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"( and to an extent Pete Buttigieg )","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"for the votes of white moderates","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"and thus further boost the left ' s odds","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"of prevailing .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"It appears Bloomberg is ignoring the naysayers","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"- and probably his own data and polling -","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"and is giving it a go after all .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":158,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent